Package: argent
Title: Argent: LLM Agents in R
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(
        given = "Marc-Aurèle",
        family = "Rivière",
        email = "marc.aurele.riviere@gmail.com", 
        role = c("aut", "cre"),
        comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-5108-3382")
    )
Description: Provides a unified R6-based interface for creating AI agents that can interact with multiple Large Language 
    Model (LLM) providers including Google Gemini, Anthropic Claude, OpenAI GPT, OpenRouter, and 
    local LLM servers. Supports chat completions, function calling, structured outputs, conversation 
    history, and advanced features like prompt caching and vector stores.
